  21 Jan 2007; Alexis Ballier <aballier@gentoo.org> dir2ogg-0.8.ebuild,
  dir2ogg-0.9.1.ebuild, dir2ogg-0.9.2.ebuild, dir2ogg-0.9.3.ebuild:
  depends on mpg123 or mpg321, bug #163026

  05 Jan 2007; Diego Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org> dir2ogg-0.8.ebuild,
  dir2ogg-0.9.1.ebuild, dir2ogg-0.9.2.ebuild, dir2ogg-0.9.3.ebuild:
  Remove src_unpack.

*dir2ogg-0.9.3 (25 Nov 2006)

  25 Nov 2006; Alexis Ballier <aballier@gentoo.org> +dir2ogg-0.9.3.ebuild:
  Version bump, thanks to Darren Kirby <bulliver@badcomputer.org>, bug #147360

  03 May 2006; Simon Stelling <blubb@gentoo.org> dir2ogg-0.8.ebuild:
  add dependency on faad; thanks to Sam Cuong Truong

  27 Apr 2006; Marien Zwart <marienz@gentoo.org> files/digest-dir2ogg-0.8,
  files/digest-dir2ogg-0.9.1, Manifest:
  Fixing SHA256 digest, pass four

*dir2ogg-0.9.2 (18 Feb 2006)

  18 Feb 2006; Tony Vroon <chainsaw@gentoo.org> +dir2ogg-0.9.2.ebuild:
  Version bump, closes bug #122068 by David Shakaryan <david@peemail.org>.
  Also added missing faad2 dependency for M4A file conversion.

  08 Jan 2006; Diego Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org> metadata.xml:
  Remove retiring dev from metadata.

  25 Jul 2005; David Holm <dholm@gentoo.org> dir2ogg-0.9.1.ebuild:
  Added to ~ppc.

*dir2ogg-0.9.1 (16 May 2005)

  16 May 2005; Jan Brinkmann <luckyduck@gentoo.org> dir2ogg-0.8.ebuild,
  +dir2ogg-0.9.1.ebuild:
  new upstream version, fixes #87626

  18 Dec 2004; Jeremy Huddleston <eradicator@gentoo.org> dir2ogg-0.8.ebuild:
  Stable amd64, sparc.

  21 Nov 2004; Jeremy Huddleston <eradicator@gentoo.org> dir2ogg-0.8.ebuild:
  Stable x86.  Added to ~amd64 and ~sparc.

*dir2ogg-0.8 (11 Oct 2004)

  11 Oct 2004; Patrick Dawson <pkdawson@gentoo.org> dir2ogg-0.8.ebuild:
